321
00:24:36,519 --> 00:24:38,254
T-Twenty-six.

322
00:24:39,622 --> 00:24:41,090
Ancient for a gold miner.

323
00:24:41,124 --> 00:24:44,561
Oh, s... no, no, see.
I-I ain't a miner.

324
00:24:44,594 --> 00:24:46,463
I-I work on a farm.

325
00:24:52,268 --> 00:24:54,204
