while you can.

338
00:25:24,534 --> 00:25:27,637
Oh, no, I can't, you see,
'cause I'm...

339
00:25:27,670 --> 00:25:30,073
- gonna marry you.
- Mm.

340
00:25:30,106 --> 00:25:32,175
You're gonna marry me?

341
