345
00:25:48,258 --> 00:25:51,094
I'm gonna give you a good life.

346
00:25:53,229 --> 00:25:55,431
Come on. Come away with me.

347
00:26:05,708 --> 00:26:06,809
Time's up.

348
00:26:06,843 --> 00:26:08,545
Come on.

349
00:26:11,514 --> 00:26:12,782
I'm coming back.

350
