Come here.

484
00:35:03,980 --> 00:35:06,849
No, no. Don't move. Don't move.

485
00:35:08,684 --> 00:35:10,653
Don't move.

486
00:35:13,256 --> 00:35:17,127
Don't make a sound.
Don't make a sound.

487
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:18,694
Look.

